=== English atom feed with xml:lang
--- input config
plugins:
  - module: Subscription::Config
    config:
      feed:
        - file://$FindBin::Bin/../../samples/guess-language/english.xml
  - module: Filter::GuessLanguage
    config:
      target: feed
--- expected
is $context->update->feeds->[0]->language, 'en';

